      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "Needs work and priced accordingly. This is a poor-condition vehicle with noticeable wear inside and out, and buyers should expect cosmetic flaws, age-related deterioration, and likely mechanical issues that will need attention. The interior shows heavy use, the exterior is rough, and it should be considered a budget car for someone who wants an inexpensive project, parts vehicle, or basic transportation with repairs expected. Please come prepared with realistic expectations, but if you're looking for a low-cost vehicle and don't mind putting work into it, it may still be worth a look.",
