      "description": "Well-kept vehicle in good overall condition. It presents nicely inside and out, with a clean exterior and tidy interior. Expect normal signs of use and some minor cosmetic wear consistent with age and mileage, but nothing that takes away from it being a solid, honest vehicle. A buyer can expect a car that has been maintained reasonably well and should make a dependable daily driver.",
