      "description": "Practical, affordable, and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward transportation for a budget-conscious buyer. It shows its age cosmetically, but it remains a solid opportunity for someone seeking dependable basic mobility without a big investment. A sensible value with room for a hands-on owner to make it their own.",
