      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly ride with plenty of life left to give? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it starts, runs, and offers a great opportunity for someone who wants reliable basic transportation without spending a fortune. It\u2019s a sensible choice for a commuter, first-time driver, or handy buyer who doesn\u2019t mind giving it a little TLC. Priced fairly and represented honestly, so you know exactly the kind of value you\u2019re getting.",
      "price": 6900.0,
